{"type": "article", "id": 5540, "title": "Herschel Supply Co. 2015 春夏系列包袋", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-26T07:19:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135231WczoSAEY3qRpZ9Kk.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tHerschel Supply Co. 在加拿大是个人气很高的包袋品牌，日前他们推出了全新的 2015 春夏系列包袋，灵感来源于中世纪的建筑风格以及沙漠气候，包括背包、托特包、手包以及旅行包等等。而为了表现这一季包袋的风格，品牌海特意取景在加州的 Palm Springs，为其拍摄 lookbook，暖色的包袋与背景暴露在加州的阳光下，蓝色格纹、卡其色与橙色交织在一起，尽显春夏风情。定价 39.99－79.99 美元（约合人民币 249－499 元）不等，<a href=\"http://shop.herschelsupply.com/collections/spring-2015\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135228orGEOD8XIwphMNPg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061352284hVpQZ6UvdNwjgDx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.34375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135229iBhbNsZfpPmFACX5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135229TIFejbwBKCmZi0uS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061352305AQ4G7KqzEBpbkZW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}